Basic je fibonacci number er recursive function ta ache er complexity holo exponential . Er mul time complexity
holo (1.618^n) . Tobe calculation er subidharte complexity O(2^n) calculate kora hoy . Ei complexity komanur 
proyojon jokhon pore thik tokhoni recursion er scene e chole ashe Dp ba Dynamic Programming .

Dp er main speciality holo jokhon amra dekhi kuno ekta recursive function eki jinish bar bar calculate kortese
tokhon amra calculate houwa value gula ekta array teh age thekei store kore rekhe dei . Jei array ta value gula
ke store kore rakhe oi array tar e FANCY NAME holo DP array . Ar ei technique tar naam holo memoization .

DP array tar size question e dewa constraints er upore nirvor kore . Sadharonoto constraints e je size dewa thake
tar cheye ektu boro ekta DP array globally newa hoy and memset use kore proti ta index e impossible value store
kore rakha hoy . Calculation er shomoy check kora hoy index e store value ta ki impossible ki na . Jodi impossible
hoy taile calculate korar proyojon pore , nahole stored value return korle e chole . Sudhu matro ei technique ta
use korar karone fibonacchi series er time complexity er value O(2^n) theke kome O(n) hoye jay . 

const int MOD = 1e5+33 ;
const int SIZE = 1e5 + 7 ;
int value[SIZE] ;
int mark[SIZE] ;

int fibonacci(int num){// Dynamic Programming er basic structure .
    // Check the base case , if the base case meets then return value .
    if(num == 0 or num == 1) return num ;
    // Check if the value is already stored in the memory or not .
    if(mark[num]) return (value[num]%MOD);
    // If the value is not stored then calculate the value and store it.
    int result = ((fibonacci(num-1)%MOD) + (fibonacci(num-2)%MOD))%MOD ;
    mark[num] = 1 ; value[num] = result%MOD ;

    return result%MOD ; // returning the value after calculating it.
}

int main(){
    Bismillah() ;

    memset(mark,0,sizeof(mark)) ;

    int n ; cin >> n ;

    cout << fibonacci(n) << sesh ;

    Alhamdulillah ;
}

Ekhane mark korar jonne alada ekta array declare na kore jodi DP name kebol ekta array declare kore ditam
and memset(dp,-1,sizeof(dp)) kore dile shompurno array er value -1 diye set hoye jeto . Tokhon amra check
kortam jodi dp[num] != -1 tahole return dp[num] . Ar nahole calculation er step e jabe .

const int SIZE = 1e5 + 7 ;
int dp[SIZE] ;
int fibonacci(int num){
    if(num == 0 or num == 1) return num ;
    if(dp[num]!=-1) return dp[num] ;
    return dp[num] = fibonacci(num-1) + fibonacci(num-2) ;
}
int main(){
    Bismillah() ;
    memset(dp,-1,sizeof(dp)) ;
    int n ; cin >> n ;
    cout << fibonacci(n) << sesh ;
    Alhamdulillah ;
}
