*) Print the digits of a given number using recursion .

Ekhane duita function lekha ache jar moddhe prothom ta recursively number er digit gula print kortese .
Ar ditiyo function er khetre backTracking er shomoy number gula print hocche . Tai first function ekok theke
boro sthaniyo maan er dike print kortese , ar second function boro value theke ekhok sthaniyo maan er dike 
print kortese .

void printDigits(ll n){                   |       void printDigits(ll n){
    if(n==0) return ;                     |            if(n==0) return ;
    cout << n % 10 << sesh ;              |            printDigits(n/10) ; 
    printDigits(n/10) ;                   |            cout << n % 10 << sesh ; 
}                                         |       }

